title: Captain Marvel # 1-4 (M.F. Enterprises)
description:
Submitted for your confusion

Here is yet another Captain Marvel in addition to the DC owned character, the Marvel owned character, and whatever other costumes cretin that was named Marvel-something

This was a four issues series published by M.F. Enterprises 1966

THIS Captain Marvel is a humanoid robot with the power to SPLIT! 

More precisely he can split his torso from his seperately controlled limbs!

You want to see that, don't you?
